{"tid":730284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假訊息累多人枉死 印度政府要求 WhatsApp 承擔責任","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:33:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"37ab4ddf4fc13d956a98f526486059152e0053f3","tid":730284,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\n自從互聯網的普及，虛假訊息的傳播比以往容易，雖然透過網絡查證消息真偽不難，但很多時人們轉發訊息前都沒有查證。之前美國總統大選期間，假新聞在 Facebook 泛濫，現在同屬 Facebook 旗下的 WhatsApp 陷入相同的苦況，被要求對印度的假訊息氾濫負起責任。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度用戶多達 2 億，是 WhatsApp 的最大市場，不過假新聞消息亦透過 WhatsApp 散播，最後釀成了悲劇。其中今年 5 月，有謠言指 Jharkhand 地區有身穿黑衣的男性在村莊之間徘徊，目的是要綁架兒童，謠言引發了恐慌，當地人對外來者開始懷疑。結果來自其他地區的商人 Haleem 和 3 名同伴駕車途經當地，未有在村民設立的檢查點停車，最後 Haleem 被村民打死。 <br />\n類似的情況還發生在印度其他地區，不少人因此枉死，原因是村民從 WhatsApp 收到謠言後信以為真，懷疑外來者是兒童綁架或活摘器官販賣的集團成員，最後被村民以私刑虐待致死。印度的電子信息技術部（MEIT）於本週二要求 WhatsApp 承擔責任，採取措施阻止虛假訊息和挑釁性內容傳播，MEIT 直指人們傳播虛假訊息，WhatsApp 難辭其咎。WhatsApp 回應指他們對事件感到震驚，會採取教育和行動作為回應，同時亦認為虛假訊息、誤傳和惡作劇需要政府、社會和科技公司攜手解決。 <br />\n來源：cnbeta <br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwuwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7e8eec91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwuwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e880f98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a> <br />\n<br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwuwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9b13c076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a> <br />\nThe post 假訊息累多人枉死 印度政府要求 WhatsApp 承擔責任 appeared first on 香港 <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwuwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4fdec2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 玩生活．樂科技."},{"pid":"7187cd14b542b0e8ae0de23ced784620f83b676f","tid":730284,"uid":58958,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"咁係散播人既錯，調轉頭要人限制過濾言論咪好搵笨？"},{"pid":"ea0becc54333aa3ab2e602d48d5282bde531fddb","tid":730284,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7187cd14b542b0e8ae0de23ced784620f83b676f","tid":730284,"uid":58958,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"咁係散播人既錯，調轉頭要人限制過濾言論咪好搵笨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"但之前唔係有柒頭話「濕疹殺父母自殺」係兒登錯咩？"},{"pid":"8f375a6bd367127d928d5eb697c25bb4a4177d0b","tid":730284,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"999b8bc5eac56dc93dd464da729277fdb9a86a79","tid":730284,"uid":113626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"無讀過書鄉下仔係咁上下."},{"pid":"efee9719952427e179719e5e42cbd58ad1fff5be","tid":730284,"uid":34927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ea0becc54333aa3ab2e602d48d5282bde531fddb","tid":730284,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7187cd14b542b0e8ae0de23ced784620f83b676f","tid":730284,"uid":58958,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"咁係散播人既錯，調轉頭要人限制過濾言論咪好搵笨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"但之前唔係有柒頭話「濕疹殺父母自殺」係兒登錯咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"所以咪就係罰d 9upper？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcaad3ffd05dc81639e1e6cef796be9a577a541","tid":730284,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔去捉友殺人嗰啲走去攪whatapp<br />\n捉一個簡單過捉一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825d35f4c5bbacf5b